<h3>Kraken</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Kraken, the world&rsquo;s leading digital asset exchange, hired Wachsman PR in January 2016, initially to announce the acquisition of Coinsetter and Cavirtex, two of the largest exchanges in North America. After weeks of planning, the announcement of perhaps the largest M&amp;A deal in bitcoin history made a major impact, and Kraken rapidly grew its customer base in the United States and Canada. In the months to come, Kraken CEO Jesse Powell became a regular fixture on Bloomberg&rsquo;s online business publication, and Kraken&rsquo;s reputation as an indispensable institution for blockchain was permanently cemented. Throughout Wachsman PR&rsquo;s continuously improving, tailor-made campaign, Kraken grew to become the heavyweight exchange, and maintained its position as the global leader for volume between Euro and crypto pairings. With Kraken&rsquo;s growth, came new token additions, new acquisitions, new business partnerships and new C-level staff hirings; WPR assisted Kraken in maximizing the coverage upon each public announcement.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
